<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.102.116196.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Morphology of Loxospora elatina (for details of specimens, see Table 1, Suppl. material 3) A, B thalli with tuberculate areoles and irregular and partly fused soralia (A UGDA L- 47757 B UGDA L- 47762) C thallus with soralia bursting from areoles and later fused (UGDA L- 47761) D soralia covering most parts of the thallus (UGDA L- 47760) E, F apothecia with sorediate or esorediate margins (O L- 97759). Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/986578" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

